description.narrative: The objective of the Project is to improve economic competitiveness by improving the capacity and quality of strategic national roads on the Borrower's islands of Java and Sumatra, improving road safety and increasing the efficiency, quality and transparency of works procurement and implementation in Borrower's Ministry of Public Works.

condition.narrative: Borrower shall carry out at regular intervals risk-based internal audits of financial controls & tech. audits of selected rd.sections to determine if construction meets specifications & tech. stds.
Borrower shall engage a Procurement Advisor in accordance with Procurement Plan and provision of LA to assist Borrower inprocurement in accordance with Procurement Plan of works for all Sub-Projects
Borrower shall engage a Procurement Agent in accordance with Procurement Plan and provisions of LA to assist the Borrower inselection and employment of the DSC, CTC and Procurement Advisor
Borrower shall engage a Public Notary to assist the Borrower in the procurement of works for Sub-Projects under WP-1 and forconsulting services where the Procurement Agent is not involved.
